name: 3D Pokemon Center
body:
### Welcome to 3D Pokemon Center Project Page.
This is a project I started in my Environment 3D class.
Is my version of a Pokemon Center in a forest. To do this project, I used the Autodesk Maya for 3D modeling and the Unity Engine to build a webgl game.
